To Install cowsay , you can use:

yum install cowsay

[ansible@bwlinux ~]$ cowsay "I love linux"
 ______________
< I love linux >
 --------------
        \   ^__^
         \  (oo)\_______
            (__)\       )\/\
                ||----w |
                ||     ||




[ansible@bwlinux ~]$ cowsay -T U Hello
 _______
< Hello >
 -------
        \   ^__^
         \  (oo)\_______
            (__)\       )\/\
             U ||----w |
                ||     ||
